  <brief_title>Safety of Capsule Endoscopy in Patients With Implantable Cardiac Devices</brief_title>
  <official_title>Safety of Capsule Endoscopy Using Human Body Communication in Patients With Cardiac Pacemakers and Implantable Cardiac Defibrillators</official_title>
  <sponsors>
